overview: Fishing Northern Baja for Yellowfin Tuna, Dorado & Yellowtail onboard the Ocean Odyssey with Owner/Operator Rick Scott on what turned out to be one of the most productive 3-day trips in recent memory. Packed with info on tackle and tips, this non-stop action features some of the best underwater dorado footage ever shot as they foamed on the hookless Orca poppers and waxwings.
title: Destination Dorado: Sea of Cortez
